---
title: Booking Flow
description: Complete user flow for booking an accommodation
author: Tech Team
date: 2025-11-06
---

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    actor User as 👤 User
    participant Web as 🌐 Web App
    participant API as 🔌 API
    participant Auth as 🔐 Better Auth Auth
    participant Service as ⚙️ BookingService
    participant DB as 🗄️ Database
    participant MP as 💳 Mercado Pago
    participant Email as 📧 Email Service

    %% Search Phase
    Note over User,Web: 1️⃣ Search Phase
    User->>Web: Enter search criteria<br/>(city, dates, guests)
    Web->>API: GET /api/v1/accommodations<br/>?city=X&checkIn=Y&checkOut=Z
    API->>Service: accommodationService.search(filters)
    Service->>DB: SELECT available accommodations
    DB-->>Service: Results
    Service-->>API: ServiceOutput<Accommodation[]>
    API-->>Web: JSON response
    Web-->>User: Display results

    %% View Details Phase
    Note over User,Web: 2️⃣ View Details Phase
    User->>Web: Click on accommodation
    Web->>API: GET /api/v1/accommodations/:id
    API->>Service: accommodationService.findById(id)
    Service->>DB: SELECT accommodation + amenities + reviews
    DB-->>Service: Accommodation details
    Service-->>API: ServiceOutput<Accommodation>
    API-->>Web: JSON response
    Web->>API: GET /api/v1/accommodations/:id/availability<br/>?checkIn=Y&checkOut=Z
    API->>Service: accommodationService.checkAvailability(id, dates)
    Service->>DB: Check existing bookings
    DB-->>Service: Availability status
    Service-->>API: ServiceOutput<boolean>
    API-->>Web: Available: true/false
    Web-->>User: Show details + availability + price

    %% Authentication Check
    Note over User,Web: 3️⃣ Authentication Phase
    User->>Web: Click "Book Now"
    Web->>Web: Check authentication
    alt Not Authenticated
        Web-->>User: Redirect to /login
        User->>Auth: Login/Signup
        Auth-->>User: Return JWT token
        User->>Web: Return to booking
    else Already Authenticated
        Note over User,Web: Continue to booking
    end

    %% Booking Form Phase
    Note over User,Web: 4️⃣ Booking Form Phase
    User->>Web: Fill booking form<br/>(dates, guests, contact info)
    Web->>Web: Validate form (TanStack Form)
    Web->>API: GET /api/v1/accommodations/:id/price<br/>?checkIn=Y&checkOut=Z&guests=N
    API->>Service: pricingService.calculatePrice(params)
    Service->>DB: Get pricing rules
    DB-->>Service: Pricing data
    Service->>Service: Calculate total<br/>(nights × price + fees + taxes)
    Service-->>API: ServiceOutput<PriceBreakdown>
    API-->>Web: Price breakdown
    Web-->>User: Show price breakdown

    %% Booking Creation Phase
    Note over User,Web: 5️⃣ Booking Creation Phase
    User->>Web: Click "Confirm Booking"
    Web->>API: POST /api/v1/bookings<br/>+ JWT token<br/>+ booking data
    API->>Auth: Verify JWT token
    Auth-->>API: Valid token + user info

    API->>Service: bookingService.create(data, actor)
    Service->>Service: Validate input (Zod)
    Service->>Service: Check permissions
    Service->>DB: BEGIN TRANSACTION

    Service->>DB: Check availability again (lock row)
    DB-->>Service: Still available

    alt Accommodation Not Available
        DB-->>Service: Not available
        Service->>DB: ROLLBACK
        Service-->>API: ServiceOutput<Error><br/>NOT_AVAILABLE
        API-->>Web: 409 Conflict
        Web-->>User: Error: Not available
    else Accommodation Available
        Service->>DB: INSERT INTO bookings<br/>(status: 'pending')
        DB-->>Service: Booking created

        %% Payment Phase
        Note over Service,MP: 6️⃣ Payment Phase
        Service->>MP: Create payment preference<br/>(amount, description, callbacks)
        MP-->>Service: Payment preference ID + init_point URL

        Service->>DB: UPDATE booking<br/>(payment_id: X, payment_url: Y)
        DB-->>Service: Updated

        Service->>DB: COMMIT TRANSACTION
        Service-->>API: ServiceOutput<Booking + payment_url>
        API-->>Web: 201 Created<br/>+ booking + payment_url
        Web-->>User: Redirect to Mercado Pago
    end

    %% Payment Completion Phase
    Note over User,MP: 7️⃣ Payment Phase
    User->>MP: Complete payment<br/>(credit card, debit, etc.)
    MP->>MP: Process payment

    alt Payment Successful
        MP->>API: POST /api/v1/webhooks/mercadopago<br/>(payment approved)
        API->>Service: bookingService.confirmPayment(payment_id)
        Service->>DB: UPDATE booking<br/>(status: 'confirmed', paid_at: NOW())
        DB-->>Service: Updated
        Service-->>API: ServiceOutput<void>
        API-->>MP: 200 OK

        %% Confirmation Phase
        Note over Service,Email: 8️⃣ Confirmation Phase
        Service->>Email: Send confirmation email<br/>- Booking details<br/>- Host contact<br/>- Check-in instructions
        Email-->>User: Confirmation email

        MP-->>User: Redirect to success page
        User->>Web: Return to /bookings/:id
        Web->>API: GET /api/v1/bookings/:id
        API->>Service: bookingService.findById(id, actor)
        Service->>DB: SELECT booking + accommodation + user
        DB-->>Service: Booking details
        Service-->>API: ServiceOutput<Booking>
        API-->>Web: JSON response
        Web-->>User: Show confirmation page

    else Payment Failed
        MP->>API: POST /api/v1/webhooks/mercadopago<br/>(payment rejected)
        API->>Service: bookingService.failPayment(payment_id)
        Service->>DB: UPDATE booking<br/>(status: 'payment_failed')
        DB-->>Service: Updated
        Service-->>API: ServiceOutput<void>
        API-->>MP: 200 OK

        MP-->>User: Redirect to failure page
        User->>Web: Return to /bookings/:id
        Web-->>User: Show payment failed message<br/>+ retry payment option
    end

    %% Error Scenarios
    Note over User,Web: ❌ Error Scenarios

    rect rgb(255, 240, 240)
        Note over Web,DB: Availability Check Failed
        Service->>DB: Check availability
        DB-->>Service: Already booked
        Service-->>API: NOT_AVAILABLE
        API-->>Web: 409 Conflict
        Web-->>User: "Sorry, no longer available"
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 240)
        Note over Web,Auth: Authentication Failed
        API->>Auth: Verify JWT
        Auth-->>API: Invalid token
        API-->>Web: 401 Unauthorized
        Web-->>User: Redirect to login
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 240)
        Note over Service,DB: Database Error
        Service->>DB: INSERT booking
        DB-->>Service: Connection error
        Service-->>API: INTERNAL_ERROR
        API-->>Web: 500 Internal Server Error
        Web-->>User: "Something went wrong, please try again"
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 240)
        Note over Service,MP: Payment Service Error
        Service->>MP: Create payment
        MP-->>Service: Service unavailable
        Service->>DB: ROLLBACK
        Service-->>API: PAYMENT_SERVICE_ERROR
        API-->>Web: 503 Service Unavailable
        Web-->>User: "Payment service unavailable, please try later"
    end
```
